    "storyEyebrow": "08 — Our story",
    "storyTitle": "Built by pool owners, for pool owners.",
    "storyAquaWord": "(aqua)",
    "storyWellWord": "(well)",
    "storyIAWord": "(intelligence)",
    "storyQuote1": "“Three roots, one promise: water done right, powered by AI.”",
    "storyQuote2": "“After 15 years, 3 different pools (concrete, shell, above-ground), 2 electrolyzers, a sand filter and a cartridge filter, hundreds of tests, dozens of bad surprises — we'd had enough.”",
    "storyQuote3": "“We tried everything: the expensive pool pro who comes once a week, basic apps that say ‘add chlorine’, forums, YouTube videos at 11pm.”",
    "storyQuote4a": "“Nothing answered the only question that matters:",
    "storyQuote4b": "“RIGHT NOW, with MY readings, MY pool, MY weather, what do I do, in what order, and when can I swim?”",
    "storyQuote5": "“AQWELIA was born from that frustration. Not by a team of marketers. By avid users sick of green water.”",
    "storyTeam": "— The AQWELIA team",
    "variationsEyebrow": "09 — A pool is alive",
    "variationsTitle": "Why does water change all the time?",
    "variationsFactor1Title": "Weather",
    "variationsFactor1Text": "Storms (dilute chlorine, shift pH), heatwaves (algae), wind (debris), frost (equipment).",
    "variationsFactor2Title": "Swimming",
    "variationsFactor2Text": "More swimmers = more organic matter = chlorine consumed faster.",
    "variationsFactor3Title": "Sunscreen",
    "variationsFactor3Text": "Phosphates and oily residue → cloudy water, algae.",
    "variationsFactor4Title": "Sweat / urine",
    "variationsFactor4Text": "Chloramines, irritating water (yes, it counts).",
    "variationsFactor5Title": "Water temperature",
    "variationsFactor5Text": "Chlorine evaporates faster when hot, chemical activity increases.",
    "variationsFactor6Title": "UV",
    "variationsFactor6Text": "Destroys unstabilized chlorine in 2h.",
    "variationsFactor7Title": "Season",
    "variationsFactor7Text": "Spring (startup), summer (intensive), fall (winterizing), winter (frost).",
    "variationsFactor8Title": "Equipment",
    "variationsFactor8Text": "Filter loading up, electrolyzer scaling, pump aging.",
