    "faqEyebrow": "12 — FAQ",
    "faqTitle": "Frequently asked questions",
    "faqContact": "Another question? Email us:",
    "faqQ1": "Does AQWELIA replace the pool professional?",
    "faqA1": "No. It complements them. The pool pro visits once a week; AQWELIA covers the other 6 days, handles emergencies, and teaches you to understand your pool. Many users keep a pool pro + AQWELIA.",
    "faqQ2": "Can the AI be wrong?",
    "faqA2": "The AI is cautious and always displays a confidence level. Critical dosage calculations are NOT done by the AI but by a deterministic engine. In case of doubt, AQWELIA says \"consult a professional\".",
    "faqQ3": "Can I use AQWELIA without a pool pro?",
    "faqA3": "Yes, that's the most common case. The app guides you step by step like a good pool pro would.",
    "faqQ4": "Is my data private?",
    "faqA4": "Yes, 100%. No resale. Your photos and measurements remain yours.",
    "faqQ5": "Does the app work offline?",
    "faqA5": "The web mode requires a connection. The native mobile app will have an offline mode for tests and logs.",
    "faqQ6": "Does AQWELIA manage spas?",
    "faqA6": "Yes! AQWELIA manages spas with dedicated features: bromine or active oxygen treatment, temperature monitoring, drain reminders, anti-evaporation covering, adapted filtration programs. Available from the Lagoon plan.",
    "faqQ7": "What if I have multiple pools?",
    "faqA7": "The Lagoon plan allows 1 pool + 1 spa, the Atlas plan is unlimited (for pool pros).",
    "faqQ8": "Can I cancel anytime?",
    "faqA8": "Yes, no commitment. No hidden fees.",
    "faqProReplace": "Does AQWELIA replace a pool professional?",
    "faqProReplaceA": "No — it complements them. The pool pro visits once a week; AQWELIA covers the other 6 days, handles emergencies, and helps you understand your water. Many users keep their pool pro and use AQWELIA alongside.",
    "faqHowIA": "How does AI analysis work?",
    "faqHowIAA": "The AI analyzes your strip, water and pool photos, combines this data with your chemical history and weather, then provides a diagnosis with a confidence level. Critical dosage calculations are performed by a deterministic engine, not by the AI.",
    "faqSpaManage": "Can I manage a spa?",
    "faqSpaManageA": "Yes. AQWELIA manages spas with dedicated features: bromine or active oxygen treatment, temperature monitoring, drain reminders and adapted filtration programs. Available from the Lagoon plan.",
    "faqSellProducts": "Does the app sell products?",
    "faqSellProductsA": "AQWELIA does not sell products directly. When a need is detected, the app recommends the right product at the right dosage, and tells you where to buy it near you. AQWELIA Care, coming soon, will automate these recommendations.",
    "faqGreenWater": "What happens if my water turns green?",
    "faqGreenWaterA": "AQWELIA detects signs of algae, identifies the likely cause (insufficient chlorine, unbalanced pH, filtration too short) and offers a step-by-step action plan: shock treatment, cleaning, pH adjustment and adapted filtration duration.",
    "faqAllYear": "Does AQWELIA work all year round?",
    "faqAllYearA": "Yes. In season, the app handles testing and dosing. During winterizing, it tells you when and how to winterize, monitors the cover, and prepares reopening in spring with a refilling plan.",
    "faqProVersion": "Is there a version for professionals?",
    "faqProVersionA": "Yes — AQWELIA Pro, coming soon, is designed for pool professionals: client and pool management, optimized scheduling, proof of visit, custom PDF reports and statistics. Sign up for early access.",
