    "pricingFaqTitle": "Frequently asked questions about pricing",
    "pricingFaqQ1": "What is success commission?",
    "pricingFaqA1": "You only pay the commission if the lead results in a billed intervention. No lead = no commission. The commission is clamped between €25 (minimum) and €150 (maximum) per won lead, regardless of the billed amount.",
    "pricingFaqQ2": "Can I change plans on the go?",
    "pricingFaqA2": "Yes, anytime. The change takes effect at the next billing cycle. If you upgrade, you immediately get the new agents.",
    "pricingFaqQ3": "Is there a commitment?",
    "pricingFaqA3": "No. All Growth OS subscriptions are commitment-free, cancelable monthly. You only pay for the current month.",
    "pricingFaqQ4": "What happens if I exceed the seat count?",
    "pricingFaqA4": "You can add extra seats at €15/seat/month on Growth Starter, €12 on Growth Pro, and unlimited on Performance.",
    "pricingFaqQ5": "Does the Performance plan include SSO?",
    "pricingFaqA5": "Yes. The Performance plan includes SSO / SAML (Okta, Google Workspace, Azure AD), the integration API, the Compliance Supervisor and onboarding support.",
